00:00:04.100 --> 00:00:08.640
In May 2007, 100 years after the opening of the world renowned zoo,

00:00:09.720 --> 00:00:18.880
 Hagenbeck gave the all-clear for its new recreational attraction: the Tropical World Adventure Aquarium.

00:00:21.520 --> 00:00:32.240
That finally gives the citizens of Hamburg and the steadily growing number of tourists to the Hanseatic city an aquarium of the highest international standard.

00:00:42.880 --> 00:00:54.680
This new attraction has given Hamburg, the waterside city and “gateway to the world“, an access to the flora and fauna of the equatorial regions.

00:01:03.280 --> 00:01:19.360
For the visitor, a truly unique world of adventure opens itself up which is designed as though Carl Hagenbeck himself had done it: with barless open enclosures, right up close to the animals.

00:01:29.640 --> 00:01:45.680
